      <title>中国股票从历史悠久的溃败中反弹，因为国家资金进入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/chinese-stocks-rebound-from-historic-rout-as-state-funds-step-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在本周开始时，中国的股票市场反弹，因为一组被称为国家队的国家有联系的资金抢购了资产，中央银行承诺贷款以帮助稳定市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/chinese-stocks-rebound-from-historic-rout-as-state-funds-step-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 01:42:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PBOC绿灯可以固定每美元7.2</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/pboc-greenlights-yuan-weakness-with-fixing-past-7-2-per-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国通过削弱了与美国的贸易战争大幅度升级的贸易战争，削弱了其日常观看7.20美元的日常参考率，从而缓解了对人民币的紧张控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/pboc-greenlights-yuan-weakness-with-fixing-past-7-2-per-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 01:19:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国州资金计划随着市场途径加深购买股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/chinese-state-funds-plan-to-buy-stocks-as-market-rout-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国支持的资金正计划购买当地股票以支持市场，这是一场与美国的贸易战争不断升级，今年侵蚀了今年的集会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/chinese-state-funds-plan-to-buy-stocks-as-market-rout-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 00:45:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>格里芬称关税为“巨大”错误伤害了中产阶级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/ken-griffin-calls-tariffs-tax-on-middle-class-and-huge-mistake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁肯·格里芬（Ken Griffin）说，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的最新关税对家庭征收巨额税，这是政府的“巨大政策错误”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/ken-griffin-calls-tariffs-tax-on-middle-class-and-huge-mistake</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 00:32:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当关税担心扫荡市场时，黄金稳定，促进避风港</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/gold-steady-as-tariff-fears-sweep-market-boost-havens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金稳定，因为担心美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的贸易战可能会冒着全球经济下滑的风险驱动避风港的需求，这表明最近几天的资产抛售暂停。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/gold-steady-as-tariff-fears-sweep-market-boost-havens</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 00:32:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚消费者情绪坠毁在特朗普关税动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/australia-consumer-sentiment-slumps-6-on-trump-tariff-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税和股票市场伴随的低迷，澳大利亚的消费者信心在四月份跌至六个月的低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/australia-consumer-sentiment-slumps-6-on-trump-tariff-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普通过冲突关税评论使投资者处于边缘状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/trump-s-clashing-tariff-comments-keep-stock-market-investors-on-edge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统威胁要以50％的进口税来拍打中国，而华盛顿和华尔街对如何从他的全球关税中获得例外感到困惑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/trump-s-clashing-tariff-comments-keep-stock-market-investors-on-edge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 00:27:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在为期三天的贸易战争之后，石油边缘更高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在经历了为期三天的低迷之后，石油的滴答速度较高，随着稍微平静的语调恢复到全球市场，交易员评估了美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的最新关税和可能的报复措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 23:21:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三星股票从新的Galaxy S25获利后跳高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/samsung-profit-beats-expectations-on-solid-demand-for-new-galaxy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三星电子公司的股票每季度利润便利地击败了对Galaxy S25智能手机和传统DRAM销售的期望，这减轻了对公司对美国关税和CHIP出口库的能力的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/samsung-profit-beats-expectations-on-solid-demand-for-new-galaxy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 22:49:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股票在有史以来最糟糕的一天后反弹：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在有记录以来最糟糕的一天之后，亚洲股票反弹，因为日本领先于期望与美国总统唐纳德·特朗普政府的贸易会谈优先考虑。国库在周一急剧抛弃后稳步，而美国股票居民期货上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 22:42:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
